## Remarks  
 The link between the value of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and the <xref:System.Data.DataTable> may be bidirectional depending on the value of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter.Direction%2A> property.  



## Examples  
 The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.  

```vb#  
Public Sub CreateOracleDbParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter()  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName"  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String  
